 carriers. Our insurance inspections\/ reports are detailed; we provide lots of photos to ensure the proper scope of work is discovered.<\/p><p>Weather its Hail, wind or fire damage City Roofing &amp; Exteriors has you covered!<\/p><p>We follow all instructions for reports requested by our carriers. But how here is how we execute an inspection:<\/p><ul><li>Take photos of the dwelling, usually 50. Photos include sites of damage, and sites of no damage.<\/li><li>We provide 10&#8217;x10&#8242; test squares from each direction of the dwelling and mark any damage within the square.<\/li><li>We take and record all the measurements of the roof, siding, eavestrough, fascia, soffit, windows and doors<\/li><li>Using our scope sheets we provide a hand drawn sketch of the dwelling, where we include measurements and sites of damage.<\/li><li>Finally we record any other concerns for underwriting: missing steps, worksite hazards, etc.<\/li><\/ul><p>For Insurance Claim Assistance please fill out a contact forum and a member of our team will be in contact with you within 24 hours<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><h3 class=\"text-center\">Insurance Services<\/h3><ul><li>Insurance Inspections<\/li><li>Insurance Reports<\/li><li>Claim Assistance<\/li><li>Underwriting Assistance<\/li><li>Estimates (Xactimate)<\/li><li>Completion of scope of work<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a53d7f4 elementor-align-left footerBtn elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"a53d7f4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/www.calgarycityroofing.com\/\/contact\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-icon\">\n\t\t\t\